,(53294,@FormName, @PK_QGroup+2,34, NULL,18,N'1',NULL,N'[1] Centralized in this context means that the cybersecurity program is coordinating necessary security patches and tracking the efforts in a single centralized location. For agencies with components (e.g., bureaus, operating divisions, components, etc.) that manage patch processes independently, this would not be considered as centralized.')
